title: Snowy Mountain Landscape
description: A breathtaking view of a snowy mountain landscape, featuring rugged peaks and a vast expanse of snow. The sky is clear and blue, with distant mountains visible on the horizon, partially obscured by clouds.

title: Coastal Area with Waves
description: An aerial view of a coastal area where waves are crashing onto the shore. The image shows a mix of water and land, with a densely populated area featuring numerous houses and greenery adjacent to the beach.

title: Lightning Strike
description: A dramatic scene depicting a lightning bolt striking down from a dark, stormy sky. The clouds are thick and ominous, with shades of blue and gray, while the landscape below features a green field and a line of trees. The contrast between the bright lightning and the dark clouds creates a striking visual effect.

title: Industrial Pollution
description: The image depicts a landscape with two large smokestacks emitting thick clouds of smoke into the sky. In the foreground, there is a green field, contrasting with the industrial structures in the background. The sky is clear with a few clouds, highlighting the pollution from the factories.
